    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Dorsal (A), ventral (B), lateral head (C), ventral right hand (D) and ventral right foot (E) views of male holotype of Megophrys kalimantanensis sp. nov. (MZB. Amph 31765 (SVLh 91.0 mm). Scale bar = 10 mm (A−B) and 5 mm (C−E)." ;
