    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Dorsal and ventral views of female paratype of Megophrys kalimantanensis sp. nov., (A) MZB. Amph 25728 (SVLh 112.5 mm) and (B) MZB. Amph 21487 (SVLh 59.6). Scale bar = 5 mm." ;
