    dc:description "FIGURE 8. Lateral (A, D), dorsal (B, E) and ventral (C, F) views of Megophrys kalimantanensis sp. nov. tadpoles (A−C) MZB. Amph 30511.1, stage 36 and (D−F) KUHE 53577, stage 45. Scale bar = 5 mm." ;
